snippet: Three people charged in a deadly salmonella outbreak traced to a southwest Georgia peanut plant five years ago will go on trial two weeks later than initially planned, a judge decided Friday....

headline.print_headline: Judge Delays Ga. Trial in Salmonella Outbreak
headline.main: Judge Delays Ga. Trial in Salmonella Outbreak

lead_paragraph: Three people charged in a deadly salmonella outbreak traced to a southwest Georgia peanut plant five years ago will go on trial two weeks later than initially planned, a judge decided Friday.
